    {
      "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80b8-9717-d86c85bc55d3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors present a new model of student behavior and an adaptive Recommender System that uses clickstream data. Their pilot intervention on edX provided adaptive learning pathways shown as a navigational suggestion. The model predicts next page where they would be likely to spend more time - based on behavior (without any ontology or assumptions). ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "18f4750c-f3ba-80b8-9717-d86c85bc55d3",
        "parent": {
